{"type":"message","id":"a596e39f","parentId":"4fc4ce19","timestamp":"2026-04-09T09:44:48.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**太好了！** `imap-smtp-email` 技能**已安装且配置完整**！\n\n### 📧 imap-smtp-email 技能状态\n\n- ✅ **文件夹存在**: `/app/skills/imap-smtp-email/`\n- ✅ **依赖已安装**: `node_modules/` 目录存在（46 个包）\n- ✅ **脚本就绪**: `setup.sh` (21KB) 和 `scripts/` 目录\n- ✅ **配置文件**: `package.json`, `SKILL.md` 齐全\n\n让我查看一下它的具体功能：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b6ac95e32548411399b72c7a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/app/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md","limit":80}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":39582,"output":171,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39753,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775727882482}}
{"type":"message","id":"297f067a","parentId":"a596e39f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T09:44:48.341Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b6ac95e32548411399b72c7a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: imap-smtp-email\ndescription: Read and send email via IMAP/SMTP. Check for new/unread messages, fetch content, search mailboxes, mark as read/unread, and send emails with attachments. Supports multiple accounts. Works with any IMAP/SMTP server including Gmail, Outlook, 163.com, vip.163.com, 126.com, vip.126.com, 188.com, and vip.188.com.\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"📧\"\n    requires:\n      bins:\n        - node\n        - npm\n---\n\n# IMAP/SMTP Email Tool\n\nRead, search, and manage email via IMAP protocol. Send email via SMTP. Supports Gmail, Outlook, 163.com, vip.163.com, 126.com, vip.126.com, 188.com, vip.188.com, and any standard IMAP/SMTP server.\n\n## Configuration\n\nRun the setup script to configure your email account:\n\n```bash\nbash setup.sh\n```\n\nConfiguration is stored at `~/.config/imap-smtp-email/.env` (survives skill updates). If no config is found there, the skill falls back to a `.env` file in the skill directory (for backward compatibility).\n\n### Config file format\n\n```bash\n# Default account (no prefix)\nIMAP_HOST=imap.gmail.com\nIMAP_PORT=993\nIMAP_USER=your@email.com\nIMAP_PASS=your_password\nIMAP_TLS=true\nIMAP_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=true\nIMAP_MAILBOX=INBOX\n\nSMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com\nSMTP_PORT=587\nSMTP_SECURE=false\nSMTP_USER=your@email.com\nSMTP_PASS=your_password\nSMTP_FROM=your@email.com\nSMTP_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=true\n\n# File access whitelist (security)\nALLOWED_READ_DIRS=~/Downloads,~/Documents\nALLOWED_WRITE_DIRS=~/Downloads\n```\n\n## Multi-Account\n\nYou can configure additional email accounts in the same config file. Each account uses a name prefix (uppercase) on all variables.\n\n### Adding an account\n\nRun the setup script and choose \"Add a new account\":\n\n```bash\nbash setup.sh\n```\n\nOr manually add prefixed variables to `~/.config/imap-smtp-email/.env`:\n\n```bash\n# Work account (WORK_ prefix)\nWORK_IMAP_HOST=imap.company.com\nWORK_IMAP_PORT=993\nWORK_IMAP_USER=me@company.com\nWORK_IMAP_PASS=password\nWORK_IMAP_TLS=true\nWORK_IMAP_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=true\nWORK_IMAP_MAILBOX=INBOX\nWORK_SMTP_HOST=smtp.company.com\nWORK_SMTP_PORT=587\nWORK_SMTP_SECURE=false\nWORK_SMTP_USER=me@company.com\nWORK_SMTP_PASS=password\nWORK_SMTP_FROM=me@company.com\n\n[195 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775727888336}}
{"type":"message","id":"17c01a94","parentId":"297f067a","timestamp":"2026-04-09T09:45:09.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📧 是的！我有 `imap-smtp-email` 技能！\n\n这是一个**功能完整的邮件客户端技能**，比 `himalaya` 更适合当前环境，因为它基于 **Node.js**（已安装），不需要额外安装二进制工具。\n\n### ✅ 当前状态\n- **技能已安装**: `/app/skills/imap-smtp-email/`\n- **依赖已就绪**: `node_modules` 已安装 (46 个包)\n- **Node/npm**: v22.22.1 / 10.9.4 ✅\n- **功能**: 支持 IMAP 收信、SMTP 发信、搜索、附件等\n\n### 🚀 功能列表\n- 📥 **收邮件**: 列出、读取、搜索邮件\n- 📤 **发邮件**: 发送纯文本或带附件的邮件\n- 🔍 **搜索**: 按发件人、主题、内容搜索\n- 🏷️ **管理**: 标记已读/未读、移动文件夹\n- 👥 **多账户**: 支持配置多个邮箱账户\n\n### ⚙️ 配置方式\n需要先配置邮箱账户信息。配置文件位置：\n- 主配置：`~/.config/imap-smtp-email/.env`\n- 备选：`/app/skills/imap-smtp-email/.env`\n\n**配置项示例**：\n```bash\n# 默认账户\nIMAP_HOST=imap.example.com\nIMAP_PORT=993\nIMAP_USER=your@email.com\nIMAP_PASS=your_password_or_app_token\nIMAP_TLS=true\n\nSMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com\nSMTP_PORT=587\nSMTP_SECURE=false\nSMTP_USER=your@email.com\nSMTP_PASS=your_password_or_app_token\nSMTP_FROM=your@email.com\n```\n\n### 💡 您想现在配置吗？\n如果您想使用这个技能，我需要知道：\n1. **邮箱类型**: 企业邮箱 (如 `niuwf@clic.com`) 还是个人邮箱？\n2. **服务器信息**: IMAP/SMTP 地址和端口（如果不知道，我可以帮您查）\n3. **认证方式**: 密码还是应用专用令牌（推荐）\n\n**或者，如果您已经有配置文件，我可以直接帮您测试功能！**\n\n需要我帮您：\n- 运行 `setup.sh` 交互式配置？\n- 检查是否已有配置？\n- 直接测试收发邮件功能？\n\n请告诉我您的需求！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":40419,"output":529,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775727888339}}
