{"type":"message","id":"b017f844","parentId":"e5853fc3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T09:47:23.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好！现在它要求输入 **IMAP Host**（IMAP 服务器地址）。\n\n对于企业邮箱（如中国人寿 `clic.com`），常见的 IMAP 服务器可能是：\n- `imap.clic.com`\n- `mail.clic.com`\n- `smtp.clic.com`（有时 IMAP 和 SMTP 相同）\n\n**请问您知道企业邮箱的 IMAP 服务器地址吗？**\n\n如果您不确定，我可以尝试：\n1. `imap.clic.com`（常见格式）\n2. 或者您提供具体的邮箱地址，我帮您推断\n\n请告诉我 IMAP 服务器地址，或者让我尝试 `imap.clic.com`？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":42825,"output":144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775728037193}}
